                           <ns1:deg/>
                           F and 26
                           <ns1:deg/>
                           F (inclusive)
                        </xs:documentation>
                        
                        
                        <xs:documentation source="CalculationsAndRules">If G04_MeasuredSuperheat is within the range of 3 deg F minimum inclusive and 26 deg F maximum inclusive then result is true. For Boolean true value display text: Measured Superheat passes CEC requirement.  Else result is false.  For Boolean false value display text: Measured Superheat does not pass CEC requirement</xs:documentation>
                        
                     
